# Pipeline Security Hardening — Build Plan & MEU Integration

## Goal

Map the 11 hardening gaps (A, B, B+, C, D, E, F, G, H, I + default template) from [retail-trader-policy-use-cases.md](file:///p:/zorivest/_inspiration/policy_pipeline_wiring-research/retail-trader-policy-use-cases.md) into the formal Zorivest build system: new build plan documents in `docs/build-plan/`, new MEUs in `BUILD_PLAN.md`, and updates to the `meu-registry.md`.

