## Resolved Questions

> [!NOTE]
> **GUI Templates page timing.** The Templates GUI is deferred to MEU-72 (scheduling GUI). MCP CRUD tools (MEU-PH9) provide agent access without GUI. Template management via the Scheduling page is the intended entry point for human users. **Decision: deferred to MEU-72.**

> [!NOTE]
> **Existing MEU modifications vs. new MEUs.** Gap A (StepContext freeze) and Gap F (variables) touch files from MEU-78/84 (✅ approved). New standalone MEUs (MEU-PH1, MEU-PH7) were created instead of reopening completed work. The new MEUs touch the same files but track as independent scope. **Decision: new standalone MEUs (option a).**

